        <fullName>FSR_Daily_Briefing_16jHn0000010ybs</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Generates a comprehensive morning briefing for a field sales rep. This is NOT a schedule or calendar view — it is a strategic briefing covering 4 sections: today&apos;s visits WITH talking points, hot items and urgent tasks, yesterday&apos;s wins and misses recap, and territory pulse metrics. Triggers: &quot;daily briefing&quot;, &quot;daily brief&quot;, &quot;morning briefing&quot;, &quot;brief me&quot;, &quot;morning update&quot;, &quot;catch me up&quot;, &quot;what&apos;s on my plate&quot; (EN), &quot;briefing quotidien&quot;, &quot;résumé du jour&quot;, &quot;quoi de neuf&quot;, &quot;brief du jour&quot; (FR), &quot;Tagesbriefing&quot;, &quot;Morgenbriefing&quot;, &quot;was steht heute an&quot; (DE), &quot;briefing giornaliero&quot;, &quot;cosa c&apos;è oggi&quot; (IT), &quot;briefing diario&quot;, &quot;qué tengo hoy&quot; (ES), &quot;デイリーブリーフィング&quot;, &quot;今日の予定&quot; (JA), &quot;일일 브리핑&quot;, &quot;오늘 일정&quot; (KO).</description>
        <developerName>FSR_Daily_Briefing_16jHn0000010ybs</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>When the user asks for a briefing in ANY language — &quot;daily briefing&quot;, &quot;daily brief&quot;, &quot;brief me&quot;, &quot;morning briefing&quot;, &quot;morning update&quot;, &quot;catch me up&quot;, &quot;what&apos;s on my plate&quot;, &quot;briefing quotidien&quot;, &quot;brief du jour&quot;, &quot;résumé du jour&quot;, &quot;Tagesbriefing&quot;, &quot;was steht heute an&quot;, &quot;briefing giornaliero&quot;, &quot;briefing diario&quot;, &quot;デイリーブリーフィング&quot;, &quot;今日の予定&quot;, &quot;일일 브리핑&quot;, &quot;오늘 일정&quot; — call FSR_Daily_Brief immediately with no inputs. The word &quot;brief&quot; or &quot;briefing&quot; ALWAYS means this action, NOT the schedule. The action gathers all relevant data automatically. Present the returned briefing directly to the user without modification.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_main</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>instruction_main</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
